  "methodology": "Tier 1: physical/theoretical scale (fixed, invariant forever — e.g. fractions/percentages/bounded ratios). Tier 2: robust empirical P2/P98 from the FROZEN reference universe (NOT per-release min/max). Values below lo → score 0; above hi → score 100. Direction set per-analysis in ANALYSIS_COMPONENTS, not here.",
